com.rulescape.odmtest.api.core

Annotation Type RuleTestSessionConfig


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface RuleTestSessionConfig
    Annotation for setting up the configuration for ODM testing decision services. Using this annotation, the properties files and the custom rule engine listeners can be configured.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.Class<? extends EngineExecutionListener>[] engineExecutionListenerClasses
      The list of custom listeners.
      java.lang.String properties
      Name of the properties file -- defaults to "ruletesting.properties".

    • Element Detail

      • engineExecutionListenerClasses

        public abstract java.lang.Class<? extends EngineExecutionListener>[] engineExecutionListenerClasses
        The list of custom listeners. These listener classes must implement EngineExecutionListener and also must have a no-argument constructor.
        Returns:
        the list of custom listeners with default of an empty list
        Default:
        {}

      • properties

        public abstract java.lang.String properties
        Name of the properties file -- defaults to "ruletesting.properties". It should be placed in the src/main/resources (i.e. in the classpath).
        Default:
        "ruletesting.properties"
